    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2380340/extras/4bb97c83c6fb671682ab077bb003cdbb.avif?t=1741709941\" width=800 height=64 /></span>You wake up in your room, feeling disoriented, with no recollection of anything.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In the midst of your confusion, you come across a person you don't recognize. Who is she, and why is she in your home?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But the central question lingers: why can't you remember anything?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >To find answers, you realize you must converse with that stranger. <strong>The decision of whether to trust her or remain cautious now lies in your hands</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2380340/extras/8386d824dcc223bd49fceed563022c49.avif?t=1741709941\" width=800 height=64 /></span><strong>- Voice acting</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>- Multiple endings for varied gameplay experiences</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>- A captivating and intriguing story</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>- Interactive storytelling that keeps players engaged</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>- Truly horrifying soundtracks that intensify the atmosphere</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>This game includes depictions of depression, anxiety, and suicide, and may not be suitable for all audiences. It is not recommended for individuals who find such topics distressing. Please take this warning seriously.</i></p>",
